om the case of the model with 100% SFE.\nThe model takes into account the estimated contamination due to the field stars\nand the Hyades-Pleiades stream, which constitutes a more limiting factor than\nthe accuracy of the Gaia measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 18:07:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-19"}
