y 0.02 eV from experiment. This work demonstrates that\nmachine learning is able to provide an accurate representation of both, the\ngeometric and the electronic structure dynamics of Li$_x$Mn$_2$O$_4$, on time\nand length scales that are not accessible by ab initio MD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 08:56:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2020 17:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-25"}
