stics as well as the cyclic turnover from disordered to ordered\nclusters and back. Such cyclic kinetic processes could represent a general\nmechanism for the maintenance of order in active matter systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 14:29:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2020 14:47:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-31"}
