ized by\nanomalous scale invariance. The overlap and interplay between these two\ncrossover behaviors is analyzed at varying temperatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 15:26:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Nov 2020 07:07:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-01"}
